REQUIREMENTS:
libcutil, https://libcutil.googlecode.com/
libglutil, https://glutil.googlecode.com/
Open Dynamics Engine (ODE), http://sourceforge.net/projects/opende/ (0.10 or later)
pkg-config for X11 glut ode

DAISIE is a C++ wrapper library for Open Dynamics Engine.

To modify install path and other local settings, Makefile.usdef should be edited.

To build,
    make
    sudo make install

After installation, try examples.
    cd example
    make
    ./ex?.exe